WEBVTT

00:06.006 --> 00:11.677
She's lost a lot of blood, but her
external injuries aren't too serious.

00:11.761 --> 00:14.638
The problem is inside her body.

17:19.538 --> 17:24.000
One is enough.
Having many will only slow me down.

23:11.973 --> 23:15.267
That was fun, Riko!
We haven't had a party in a while!

23:15.352 --> 23:18.687
And Tozawa-chan took lots of pictures for us!

23:18.772 --> 23:20.815
Let's put some in the
kitchen when they're done!

23:20.899 --> 23:26.362
I like being with you, Riko!
I really, really like it!

23:26.446 --> 23:28.739
I want to always see your face!

23:28.824 --> 23:32.284
Not when you're crying; when you're smiling.

23:32.369 --> 23:35.454
I want you to always be able to smile.

23:35.539 --> 23:38.874
That's the only thing I wish for now.
